snippet.title: Black Skylands - Official Animated Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2021
snippet.description:
Prepare to set sail through the skies in Black Skylands. Build your skyship and explore the open world, fight factions of pirates and monsters, claim your territory by foot or by your flying vessel. You're the captain and the sky's the limit in this skypunk Open World action adventure.

#IGN #Gaming #SummerOfGaming
